         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Justus Perthes' geographical Institution. ¶ Publishing Firm of Petermanns Intercommunication. ¶ Gotha 19 June 1888 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I have the intention of publishing in the next Edition of the 'Gotha Geogr...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">88.06.19</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From H. Wichmann</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS <seg style="background-color: #ffff00; ">M</seg>
               <seg style="font-weight: bold; background-color: #ffff00; ">number</seg>, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof. PS. 28/8/08.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">
                  <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Justus Perthes' Geographische Anstalt</seg>
               </seg>
               <seg style="font-style: italic; ">.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">
                  <seg style="">Redaktion von Petermanns Mitteilungen</seg>
               </seg>
               <seg>.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">
                  <seg style="">Gotha, den</seg>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> 19 juin </seg>
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">
                  <seg style="">18</seg>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">88</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Monsieur,</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>J'ai l'intention de publier dans la prochaine édition de l'Annuaire géographique de Gotha, qui paraîtra cet été sous la rédaction de M. le Dr. H. Wagner, professeur à l'université de Goettingen, un resumé sur les sociétés de géographie et leurs travaux, comme je l'ai fait dans les années précedentes de cet ouvrage mentionné. </seg>Pour cela j'ai l'honneur de vous demander quelques notices statistiques sur l'état actuel de votre société, et je vous prie de me renvoyer la feuille ci-jointe le plus tôt possible après y avoir fait vos remarques aux questions, qui y sont posées.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Aussitôt que mon article sera publié je m'empresserai de vous en envoyer un exemplaire.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Veuillez agréer, Monsieur, l'assurance de ma considération la plus distinguée</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">H. Wichmann</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">Justus Perthes' geographical Institution.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">This translation is written on the letter in a 19th-century hand, with the following note appended:</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.639in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; "
                     xml:lang="en">Questions to be answered:</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.639in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; "
                     xml:lang="en">1. What is the present number of Members?</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.639in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; "
                     xml:lang="en">2. What was the last statement of total receipts?</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.639in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; "
                     xml:lang="en">3. Does the Society receive any subsidy from the Government, Municipality or Chamber of Commerce etc.</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.639in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; "
                     xml:lang="en">4. What Capital have you?</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.639in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; "
                     xml:lang="en">5. What kind of publications do you issue (Bulletins, Revues etc) in your Society? </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Publishing Firm of Petermanns Intercommunication.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Gotha 19 June 1888</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the intention of publishing in the next Edition of the 'Gotha Geographical Annual'<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Geographisches Jahrbuch</seg>, published by the Perthes publishing house.</p>
               </note> which will appear this summer edited by Dr. H. Wagner professor of the University of Göttingen an abridged account of all geographical societies and their transactions as I have done in the preceding numbers of the above mentioned Annual. I would therefore ask you for some statistics on the present state of your Society and should feel obliged if you would reply to the subjoined questions, adding any remarks you think proper, and would return me the paper with the briefest possible delay.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I shall send you a copy of the article as soon as it is published.<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Wichmann (1888); see pp. 468, 470 for the information relating to the Royal Geographical Society of Australasia, Victorian Branch.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Yours etc</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">H. Wichmann</p>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
